                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00R296/4380: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Hoover</persName> to President
                            <persName type="to">von Hindenburg</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-09">July 9,
                            1931</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have received with great appreciation your communication of July 7. It is my
                    sincere hope and expectation that this proposal which has been presented to and
                    accepted by the nations of the world will revive confidence and promote
                    prosperity among all peoples.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herbert Hoover</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
